=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">charge</tr_> them . . , <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:113\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.113</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰ παραπτώματα λ. τινί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0031.tlg008.perseus-grc1:5:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">2 Ep.Cor.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.19</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n63713.3\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">audit the accounts of</tr_> a person, c. dat., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τοῖς ὑπευθύνοις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg003.perseus-grc1:54:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">54.2</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταῖς ἀρχαῖς</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg003.perseus-grc1:48:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48.3</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n63713.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> without reference to numbers, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">take into account, calculate, consider</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ταῦτα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.53</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:816\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"au